{
  "texts": [
    "A rise in publication trends has been identified.",
    "Researchers who integrate AI into language learning use a variety of tools, leading to the formation of new fields within the field and new branches within AI-based language learning.",
    "This, in turn, is speculated to be a major reason for the decline in citation trends.",
    "However, the constructive viewpoint regarding this aspect is that the researchers, utilizing diverse AI-based tools, are expected to contribute significantly to the field.",
    "Affirming this, documents that were published during 2017 and 2018 are identified, through bibliographic coupling, to be 'often cited' papers indicating their mark as foundational works."
  ]
}